---
import MainLayout from "../../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Muscle Gain Program | Transform">
  <div class="container mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Muscle Gain Program</h1>
    <p class="mb-6">Build strength, size, and definition with our specialized muscle gain program.</p>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>Our Muscle Gain program focuses on progressive resistance training, proper recovery protocols, and optimal nutrition to help you build lean muscle mass efficiently. Whether you're looking to increase overall muscle size or develop specific muscle groups, our expert trainers will guide you through the process.</p>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Program Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Strength and body composition assessment</li>
        <li>Progressive resistance training programming</li>
        <li>Recovery and mobility protocols</li>
        <li>Nutrition planning for muscle growth</li>
        <li>Regular progress tracking and program adjustments</li>
      </ul>
      
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-primary-dark transition">Book a Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
